Package org.jLOAF.preprocessing.filter.casebasefilter

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActionClustering
    this class clusters the CaseBase based on the number of actions the domain used has.
    BucketNode  
    Clustering
    this class is used to cluster casebases, it puts similar cases in one cluster,the picks one of them to add it to the new casebase removing almost duplicated cases
    FullClustering  
    KClustering  
    KDTree  
    NoFilter  
    Sampling
    Preprocess the CaseBase by only adding a case into the CaseBase if the prediction of the action using the current CaseBase is wrong return the new CaseBase
    UnderSampling
    This class undersamples the majority class by randomly removing a percentage of the majority class cases based on the value of underSamplePercent which can range from [0,1] where 1 represents equalizing the majority and minority classes, and 0 represents not removing cases.
